We could, but I'm not sure we should, although I don't really have that strong opinion about it. We should be careful about having sugar that doesn't really save that much typing and it gives the user multiple ways to do one thing.

The point of having a powerful .require method is that they can do all the loading in one method. If we introduce the .add sugar. User will start to do this:

